      "options": {
        "content": "## Email Delivery Overview\nThis dashboard is backed by the notification business events already emitted by `BackendProjectTemplate.Consumer`.\n\n### Queryable email delivery events today\n- `EmailNotificationSent`\n- `EmailNotificationDelivered`\n\n### Drilldown dimensions\n- `provider_key`\n- `notification_type`\n\nDelivery rate is computed as delivered emails divided by sent emails for the selected time range.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Current Email Event Scope",
      "type": "text"
    },
